Package org.eclipse.imagen.media.jiffle.parser

Interface JiffleListener

All Superinterfaces:
ParseTreeListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseWorker, ExpressionWorker, ImagesBlockWorker, InitBlockWorker, JiffleBaseListener, OptionsBlockWorker, PropertyWorker, RuntimeModelWorker, SourcePositionsWorker, VarWorker
public interface JiffleListener extends ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by JiffleParser.
